00:17:45.230 --> 00:17:46.760
to get this one right there.

00:17:46.760 --> 00:17:47.697
AUDIENCE: OK.

00:17:47.697 --> 00:17:48.530
MICHAEL SHORT: Yeah.

00:17:48.530 --> 00:17:49.883
So this way, we have--

00:17:49.883 --> 00:17:51.800
in this case, we had,
