00:18:54.380 --> 00:18:55.520
Let me stick that in there.

00:19:00.000 --> 00:19:01.980
L, i.

00:19:01.980 --> 00:19:02.580
Yep.

00:19:02.580 --> 00:19:03.080
Yeah.

